Yeshiva University transferred the ownership of Einstein to Montefiore since 2015, not 2018. (Yeshiva University still continued to confer Einstein degrees for a few years, but it was more like an affiliation and the parental institute has been Montefiore since 2015. This has been almost 10 years: The relationship between Einstein and Yeshiva is mentioned in the History section, and should not be displayed in this box as a distraction.
